  • News  ●○

    The mid-2021 population of Brazil is estimated as 213.3 million. The next population census is postponed to 2022.

    2021-08-28

    The mid-2020 population of Brazil is estimated as 211.8 million. With a growth of 4.2%, Roraima was the fastest-growing state between 2019 and 2020. Piauí had with 0.25% the smallest increase in the same period.

    2020-08-29
